-- Harviz of Romania Offers Contract to Upgrade Town Water Plants
-- B y   I r i n a   S a v u
-- 2013-04-24T11:53:33Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-04-24/harviz-of-romania-offers-contract-to-upgrade-town-water-plants.html
Harviz SA , a Romanian utility, is
seeking bids for a 26.9 million lei ($8 million) to 29.3 million
lei contract to upgrade water plants in the county of Harghita.  The utility plans to improve and expand water-treatment
plants in the central towns of Madaras and Vlahita and is
accepting bids for the 21-month contract to June 17, according
to a  document  posted today on the European Union tender website.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Irina Savu in Bucharest at 
 isavu@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James M. Gomez at 
 jagomez@bloomberg.net  